      • modifySecurityAction

        protected int modifySecurityAction(int oldAction)
        Description copied from class: ResourcePermission
        Change security action, stored in DB to real security action, used by system. This mainly helps during migration process when you want to modify security action to another value. Say, change INT_ADMIN from 0x7 to 0xFFF3

        modifySecurityAction in class ResourcePermission
        Parameters:
